+ public_name: Ноунейм (string) - the name to show on public sources
+ type: MSP (string) - type of legal entity [MSP/PHARMACY]. MIS can't be created using this WS.
+ owner_property_type: STATE (string) - Dictionary OWNER_PROPERTY_TYPE
+ legal_form: 140 (string) - Dictionary LEGAL_FORM
+ edrpou: 5432345432 (string) -  Unified Register of Businesses and Organizations
