### Job_Error_403
+ error: Error description (string) - Human-readable error message.
+ eta: 2018-08-02T10:45:16.000Z (string) - estimated time of arrivals
+ status: failed (string) - status of request processing
+ status_code: 403 (string) - processing result

### Job_Error_404
+ error (object) - Error description
    + type: Error_type (string) - Atom that represents error type.

### Job_Error_409
+ error (object) - Error description
    + message: Error description (string) - Human-readable error message.
    + type: Error_type (string) - Atom that represents error type.
+ eta: 2018-08-02T10:45:16.000Z (string) - estimated time of arrivals
+ status: failed (string) - status of request processing
+ status_code: 409 (string) - processing result

### Job_Error_422
+ status: failed (string) - status of request processing
+ status_code: 422 (string) - processing result
+ error (Response__Error_ValidationFailed, required)
+ eta: 2019-04-26T09:16:15.936 (string) 

### Link
+ entity: job (string) - name of the entity that link follows to
+ href: /Jobs/NBXk9EyErUZv1RhXgyvgg (string) - link to entity

### Reference_request
+ identifier (Identifier)

### Reference_response
+ identifier (Identifier)
+ display_value: null (string) - This field is required in the Reference, so it may be returned empty.

### Reference
+ identifier (Identifier)

### Identifier
+ type(Codeable_Concept, required) - Description of identifier
+ value : 9183a36b-4d45-4244-9339-63d81cd08d9c (string)- The value that is unique

### Codeable_Concept
+ coding (array, required)
    + (object)
        + include Coding
+ text (string)

### Coding
+ system : eHealth/resources (string)
+ code : patient (string) - Symbol in syntax defined by the system

### Period
+ start : 2018-08-02T10:45:16.000Z(string, required) - Starting time with inclusive boundary
+ end : 2018-08-02T11:00:00.000Z(string, optional) - End time with inclusive boundary, if not ongoing

### Quantity
+ value : 13,5 (number, required)
+ comparator : > (string)
+ unit : kg (string) - for future use
+ system : eHealth/ucum/units (string)
+ code: kg (string)

### Range
+ low (Quantity, required)
+ high (Quantity, required)

### Timing
+ event: 2018-08-02T10:45:16.000Z
+ repeat (object)
    + include Repeat
+ code: TIMING_ABBREVIATION (string)

### Repeat
+ count: 10 (string) - Number of times to repeat
- One Of
    + bounds_duration (Quantity, optional)
    + bounds_range (Range, optional)
    + bounds_period (Period, optional)
+ count_max: 20 (string) - Maximum number of times to repeat
+ duration: 15 (string) - How long when it happens
+ duration_max: 25 (string) - How long when it happens
+ duration_unit: UNITS_OF_TIME (string) - unit of time dictionary
+ frequency: 1 (string) - Event occurs frequency times per period
+ requency_max: 4 (string) - Event occurs up to requency max times per period
+ period: 1 (string) - Event occurs frequency times per period
+ period_max: 3 (string) - Upper limit of period, 3-4 hours
+ period_unit: UNITS_OF_TIME (string) - unit of time dictionary
+ day_of_week: DAYS_OF_WEEK (string) - DAYS OF WEEK dictionary
+ time_of_day: 15:30 (string) - Time of day for action
+ when: EVENT_TIMING (optional) - Code for time period of occurrence
+ offset: 20 (string) - Minutes from event, before or after

# ## Specimen

### Specimen_Collection_Request
+ collector (Reference_request, required) - Who collected the Specimen.
    + identifier (Identifier, required)
        + type (Codeable_Concept)
            + coding (array)
                + (Coding)
                    + code: employee (enum)
                        - employee
                        - patient
- One Of
    + collected_date_time: 2023-04-20T19:14:13Z (string) - The time when Specimen was collected. ISO 8601 date and time in UTC timezone.
    + collected_period (object) - The period of time during which the Specimen was collected
        + start : 2023-04-20T10:45:16.000Z(string, required) - Starting time with inclusive boundary
        + end : 2023-04-20T11:00:00.000Z(string, optional) - End time with inclusive boundary, if not ongoing
+ duration (object) - How long it took to collect Specimen
    + value: 5 (number, required)
    + system: eHealth/ucum/units (string)
    + code: min (string)
    + comparator: > (string)
+ quantity (object) - The quantity of specimen collected
    + value: 20 (number, required)
    + system: eHealth/ucum/units (string)
    + code: g (string)
+ method (Codeable_Concept, optional) - Technique used to perform collection
    + coding (array)
        + (Coding)
            + system: specimen_collection_methods (string)
            + code: default (string)
+ body_site (Codeable_Concept, optional) - Anatomical collection site
    + coding (array)
        + (Coding)
            + system: eHealth/body_sites (string)
            + code: head (string)
+ fasting_status_codeable_concept (Codeable_Concept, optional) - Whether or how long patient abstained from food and/or drink
    + coding (array)
        + (Coding)
            + system: fasting_statuses (string)
            + code: default (string)


### Specimen_Container_Request
+ identifier: 1-3244-ABC (string) - Id for the container
+ description: Some container description (string) - Textual description of the container
+ type (Codeable_Concept, required) - Kind of container directly associated with specimen.
    + coding (array)
        + (Coding)
            + system: specimen_container_types (string)
            + code: default (string)
+ capacity (object) - Container volume or size
    + value: 30000 (number, required)
    + system: eHealth/ucum/units (string)
    + code: mg (string)
+ specimen_quantity (object) - Quantity of specimen within container
    + value: 20 (number, required)
    + system: eHealth/ucum/units (string)
    + code: g (string)
+ additive_codeable_concept (Codeable_Concept, optional) - Additive associated with container.
    + coding (array)
        + (Coding)
            + system: specimen_container_additives (string)
            + code: default (string)

### Specimen_Request
+ id: b075f148-7f93-4fc2-b2ec-2d81b19a9b7b (string) - Specimen Identifier
+ status: available (string) - status of the Specimen according to specimen_statuses
+ type (Codeable_Concept, required)
    + coding (array)
        + (Coding)
            + system: specimen_types (string)
            + code: default (string)
+ condition (Codeable_Concept, optional) - State of the specimen.
    + coding (array)
        + (Coding)
            + system: specimen_conditions (string)
            + code: default (string)
+ note: Some notes (string) - Comments
+ managing_organization (Reference_request, required) - Legal entity where the specimen was created
    + identifier (Identifier)
        + type (Codeable_Concept)
            + coding (array)
                + (Coding)
                    + code: legal_entity (string)
+ registered_by (Reference_request, required) - Who registered the specimen.
    + identifier (Identifier, required)
        + type (Codeable_Concept)
            + coding (array)
                + (Coding)
                    + code: employee (string)
+ parent (array, optional) - Specimens from which this Specimen originated
    + (Reference_request)
        + identifier (Identifier)
            + type (Codeable_Concept)
                + coding (array)
                    + (Coding)
                        + code: specimen (string)
+ request (array, optional) - Service requests on diagnostic, represents why the Specimen was collected.
    + (Reference_request)
        + identifier (Identifier)
            + type (Codeable_Concept)
                + coding (array)
                    + (Coding)
                        + code: service_request (string)
+ collection (Specimen_Collection_Request, required) - Collection details
+ container (array, required) - Direct container of Specimen 
    + (Specimen_Container_Request)

### Specimen_EDP_Request
+ include Specimen_Request
+ context (Reference_request, required)
    + identifier (Identifier)
        + type (Codeable_Concept)
            + coding (array)
                + (Coding)
                    + code: encounter (string)
+ collection (Specimen_Collection_Request, required) - Collection details
    + procedure (Reference_request, optional) - Procedure that collects the specimen.
        + identifier (Identifier, required)
            + type (Codeable_Concept)
                + coding (array)
                    + (Coding)
                        + code: procedure (string)
+ received_time: 2023-04-20T19:14:13Z (string) - The time when Specimen was received for processing
+ status: available (enum) - status of the Specimen according to specimen_statuses
    - available
    - unavailable
+ status_reason (Codeable_Concept, optional) - in case the Specimen has unavailable status
    + coding (array)
        + (Coding)
            + system: specimen_invalidate_reasons (string)
            + code: used (string)

### Specimen_Response
+ include Specimen_Request
+ status: available (enum) - status of the Specimen according to specimen_statuses
    - available
    - unavailable
    - unsatisfactory
    - entered_in_error
+ managing_organization (Reference_response, required) - Legal entity where the Specimen was created
    + identifier (Identifier)
        + type (Codeable_Concept)
            + coding (array)
                + (Coding)
                    + code: legal_entity (string)
    + display_value: Комунальне підприємство Медлаб (string) - This field is filled on creating and never updated after
+ registered_by (Reference_response, required) - Who registered the Specimen.
    + identifier (Identifier, required)
        + type (Codeable_Concept)
            + coding (array)
                + (Coding)
                    + code: employee (string)
    + display_value: Тарасенко Максим Петрович (string) - This field is filled on creating and never updated after
+ context (Reference_response, optional) - Encounter if Specimen created using EDP.
    + identifier (Identifier, required)
        + type (Codeable_Concept)
            + coding (array)
                + (Coding)
                    + code: encounter (string)
+ accession_identifier: AX64-654T-X654-AX65 (string) - Human readable requisition number
+ received_time: 2023-04-20T19:14:13Z (string) - The time when Specimen was received for processing. ISO 8601 date and time in UTC timezone.
+ parent (array, optional) - Specimens from which this Specimen originated
    + (Reference_response)
        + identifier (Identifier)
            + type (Codeable_Concept)
                + coding (array)
                    + (Coding)
                        + code: specimen (string)
+ request (array, optional) - Service requests on diagnostic, represents why the Specimen was collected.
    + (Reference_response)
        + identifier (Identifier)
            + type (Codeable_Concept)
                + coding (array)
                    + (Coding)
                        + code: service_request (string)
+ subject (Reference_response, required)
    + identifier (Identifier)
        + type (Codeable_Concept)
            + coding (array)
                + (Coding)
+ status_reason (Codeable_Concept)
    + coding (array)
        + (Coding)
            + system (enum)
                - specimen_reject_reasons
                - specimen_invalidate_reasons
                - specimen_cancel_reasons
            + code: default (string)
+ collection (Specimen_Collection_Request, required) - Collection details
    + collector (Reference_response, required) - Who collected the Specimen.
        + identifier (Identifier, required)
            + type (Codeable_Concept)
                + coding (array)
                    + (Coding)
                        + code: employee (enum)
                            - employee
                            - patient
        + display_value: Василенко Олена Павлівна (string) - This field is filled on creating and never updated after
    + duration (object) - How long it took to collect Specimen
        + value: 5 (number, required)
        + system: eHealth/ucum/units (string)
        + code: min (string)
        + comparator: > (string)
        + unit: хв (string)
    + quantity (object) - The quantity of Specimen collected
        + value: 20 (number, required)
        + system: eHealth/ucum/units (string)
        + code: g (string)
        + unit: грам (string)
    + procedure (Reference_response, optional) - Procedure that collects the Specimen.
        + identifier (Identifier, required)
            + type (Codeable_Concept)
                + coding (array)
                    + (Coding)
                        + code: procedure (string)
+ container (array, required) - Direct container of Specimen 
    + (Specimen_Container_Request)
        + capacity (object) - Container volume or size
            + value: 30000 (number, required)
            + system: eHealth/ucum/units (string)
            + code: mg (string)
            + unit: міліграм (string)
        + specimen_quantity (object) - Quantity of Specimen within container
            + value: 20 (number, required)
            + system: eHealth/ucum/units (string)
            + code: g (string)
            + unit: грам (string)
+ inserted_at: 2017-04-20T19:14:13Z (string) - ISO 8601 date and time in UTC timezone.
+ inserted_by: e1453f4c-1077-4e85-8c98-c13ffca0063e (string)
+ updated_at: 2017-04-20T19:14:13Z (string) - ISO 8601 date and time in UTC timezone.
+ updated_by: 2922a240-63db-404e-b730-09222bfeb2dd (string)  

