### Program_medications_for_Qualify
+ id: 0f2fbf93-3041-4c0d-a3cf-ff558c861df8 (string) - Program participant identifier
+ medication_id: 59781de0-2e64-4359-b716-bcc05a32c10f(string, required) -  Medication Identifier
+ medication_name: Амлодипін-КВ  (string) - Medication name
+ form: PILL (string) - Dictionary MEDICATION_FORM
+ manufacturer (Manufacturer, optional)
+ reimbursement_amount: 15 (number) - Amount to reimburse for one medication_unit by medical_program
+ wholesale_price: 25.14 (number) - Wholesale pricing per package, UAH
+ consumer_price: 34.03 (number) - Retail price for packaging, UAH
+ reimbursement_daily_dosage: 1.4438 (number) - The amount of the compensation of the daily dose of the medical product, UAH
+ estimated_payment_amount: 5.15 (number) - Amount of additional payment for packing, UAH
+ container_dosage (Dosage_container, optional)
+ package_min_qty: 20 (number) - indivisible part of medicine pacage
+ package_qty: 20 (number) - quantity of medicine in a pacage
+ start_date: 2019-01-01 (string) - Active from date
+ end_date: 2019-06-30 (string) - Active to date
+ registry_number: REG-1111 (string) - Registry number
+ drlz_sku_id: 0404466792737630283703997321 (string) - identifier of a product out of external DRLZ register 
+ package_qty_divisible: true (boolean) - package divisible flag

