# ## Dictionaries

### Dictionary
+ name: DOCUMENT_TYPE (string) - Unique dictionary name
+ values (object)
    + key: value (string) - List of dictionary entries as Key:Value pairs
+ labels (array)
    - SYSTEM
    - EXTERNAL
+ is_active: true (boolean)

### Dictionary_value
+ code: b1142 (string) - code of the dictionary value
+ description: Орієнтація в особі (string) - description of the code
+ is_active: true (boolean) - status of the dictionary value
+ child_values(array) - subordinate values of the dictionary

### Dictionary_v2
+ name: eHealth/ICF/classifiers (string) - Unique dictionary name
+ description: Класифікатори МКФ (string) - dictionary description for a user
+ values (array, required)
    + (Dictionary_value)
        + child_values (array)
            + (object)
                + include Dictionary_value
                + code: b11429 (string) - code of the dictionary value
                + description: Орієнтація в особі неуточнена (string) - description of the code
+ labels (array)
    - SYSTEM
    - EXTERNAL
+ is_active: true (boolean)


