# ## Person_details

### Person_identity
+ last_name: Іванов (string) - full surname of the patient
+ first_name: І. (string) - short format of the patient's first name with the dot
+ second_name: І. (string) - short format of the patient's second name with the dot
+ gender (enum) - gender of the patient, value from the dictionary GENDER
    - MALE
    - FEMALE
        - MALE
+ age: 35 (number, required) - full years between inserted_at and birth date

# ## Procedures

### Procedure_Request
+ id: 90a9e15b-b71b-4caf-8f2e-ff247e8a5600 (string) - Unique procedure identifier 
+ based_on (Reference_request, optional) - reference to [Service Request](https://ehealthmedicaleventsapi.docs.apiary.io/#reference/service-requests); One of (based_on OR paper_referral) is required
    + identifier (Identifier)
        + type (Codeable_Concept)
            + coding (array)
                + (Coding)
                    + code: service_request (string)
+ paper_referral (Paper_referral, optional) - One of (based_on OR paper_referral) is required
+ status : completed (enum) - Status for provided procedure
    - completed
    - entered_in_error
+ status_reason (Codeable_Concept, optional) - Reason why current status was set to procedure. Is mandatory for entered_in_error
    + coding (array)
        + (Coding)
            + system: eHealth/procedure_status_reasons (string)
            + code: default (string)
+ code (Reference_request, required) - code of procedure
    + identifier (Identifier)
        + type (Codeable_Concept)
            + coding (array)
                + (Coding)
                    + code: service (string)
- One Of
    - performed_date_time: 2018-08-02T10:45:16.000Z (string) - date and time when the procedure have been performed
    - performed_period (object , optional) - is required if procedure based on service request with quantity that has code=MINUTE (system=SERVICE_UNIT)
        + start: 2018-08-02T10:45:16.000Z (string)
        + end: 2018-08-12T10:45:16.000Z (string) 
+ recorded_by (Reference_request, required) - employee who submit procedure to e-Health
    + identifier (Identifier, optional)
        + type (Codeable_Concept, required)
            + coding (array, required)
                + (Coding)
                    + code: employee (string)
+ primary_source: true (boolean) - source of procedure information. True - the procedure is done by current doctor, false - according to someone description.
- One Of
    - performer (object) - if primary_source=true
        + identifier (object)
            + type (object)
                + coding (array, optional)
                    + (object)
                        + system: eHealth/resources (string)
                        + code: employee (string)
                + text: Галина Олександрівна (string)
            + value: 97d57238-ffbe-4335-92ea-28d4de117ea2 (string)
    - report_origin (object) - if primary_source=false
        + coding (array, optional)
            + (object)
                + system: eHealth/report_origins (string)
                + code: mother (string)
        + text: зі слів пацієнта (string)
+ division (Reference_request, optional) - Division of legal_entity where procedure have been performed.
    + identifier (Identifier)
        + type (Codeable_Concept)
            + coding (array)
                + (Coding)
                    + code: division (string)
+ managing_organization (Reference_request, required) - Organization where procedure have been performed. Reference to legal_entity
    + identifier (Identifier)
        + type (Codeable_Concept)
            + coding (array)
                + (Coding)
                    + code: legal_entity (string)

+ reason_references (array, optional) - The justification of why the procedure was performed.
    + (Reference_request)
        + identifier (Identifier)
            + type (Codeable_Concept)
                + coding (array)
                    + (Coding)
                        + code: condition (string)
                        
+ outcome (Codeable_Concept, optional) - The outcome of the procedure
    + coding (array)
        + (Coding)
            + system: eHealth/procedure_outcomes (string)
            + code: default_outcome (string)
            
+ note: Додаткова інформація по процедурі (string) - Any other notes and comments about the procedure.
+ category (Codeable_Concept, required) - Classification of the procedure
    + coding (array)
        + (Coding)
            + system: eHealth/procedure_categories (string)
            + code: default (string)

+ used_codes (array,optional)
    + (Codeable_Concept)
        + coding (array)
            + (Coding)
             + system: eHealth/assistive_products (string) 
             + code: 03_05_38 (string)
             
+ used_references (array, optional) - Items used during procedure.
    + (Reference_request)
        + identifier (Identifier)
            + type (Codeable_Concept)
                + coding (array)
                    + (Coding)
                        + code: equipment (string)                


