### Program_device
+ id: 0f2fbf93-3041-4c0d-a3cf-ff558c861df8 (string) - Program participant identifier
+ device_definition(Device_Definition_base, required) -  Device definition
+ reimbursement (object) - Information about reimbursement by the program
   + type: FIXED (string) - reimbursement type according to REIMBURSEMENT_TYPE dictionary
   + percentage_discount: 12.45 (number) - Percent of a discount. Applicable only if type PERCENTAGE
   + reimbursement_amount: 50.98 (number) - Amount to reimburse for one device by medical_program. Applicable only if type FIXED
+ wholesale_price: 25.14 (number) - Wholesale pricing per package, UAH
+ consumer_price: 34.03 (number) - Retail price for packaging, UAH
+ reimbursement_daily_count: 5 (number) - The daily count of the device definition to be compensated
+ estimated_payment_amount: 5.15 (number) - Amount of additional payment for packing, UAH
+ max_daily_count: 10 (number) - The maximum allowable daily quantity of the device
+ registry_number: REG-1111 (string) - Registry number
+ start_date: 2019-01-01 (string) - Active from date
+ end_date: 2019-06-30 (string) - Active to date

### Device_Definition_base
+ id: 3e34da3d-9b8c-4aaf-be8e-24a161279b6a (string) - Unique identifier of Device definition
+ device_names (array [device_name], required)
+ classification_type: 30221 (string) - Classification type. Dictionary device_definition_classification_type
+ manufacturer (Manufacturer, optional)
+ model_number: M23N76 (string) - Model number
+ packaging (Device_definition_package, required)

### device_name
+ name: Тест-смужки Accu-Chek Active для глюкометра (string) - Device name
