+ external_id: 123-ASD-#1 (string) - Identifier from external system
+ udi (array, optional) - A set of unique identifiers assigned to the asset by the manufacturer 
    + (object)
        + value: IMEI 49015420323751 (string) - udi identifier
        + type: default (string) - type of the udi identifier acording to dictionary EQUIPMENT_UDI_TYPE
        + assigner_name: Ukrainian center of the certification (string) - assigner name of the udi
+ lot_number: RZ12345678 (string)
+ manufacturer: GlobalMed, Inc (string)
+ manufacture_date: 1999-01-01 (string)
+ expiration_date: 2020-01-01 (string)
+ model_number: NSPX30 (string)
+ part_number: #e30-SD (string)
+ version: v1.0.1 (string)
+ name: Рентген апарат флюрографічній (string)
+ serial_number: S/N234554 (string)
+ note: Технічний огляд раз на рік (string)

