### contract_legal_entity_details
+ id: df9f70ee-4b12-4740-b0f5-bb5aea116863 (string) - legal entity ID which make contract request
+ name: Клініка Ноунейм (string) - full official name of legal entity also the name to show on public sources [as map,portal etc]
+ edrpou: 32323454 (string) - Unified Register of Businesses and Organizations
+ addresses (array[Address], required) - The max items of array is 2: REGISTRATION - required, RESIDENCE - optional. DIVISION is exception: REGISTRATION - optional, RESIDENCE - required

### Payment_details
+ bank_name: Банк номер 1 (string) - bank name
+ MFO: 351005 (string) - bank code, required for account number
+ payer_account: 32009102701026 (string) - Account number or International Bank Account Number


### Contractor_divisions
+ id: 2922a240-63db-404e-b730-09222bfeb2dd (string) - division ID
+ name: Бориспільське відділення Клініки Ноунейм (string) - the full name of division
+ addresses (array[Address], required)
+ phones (array[Phone], required)
+ email: email@example.com (string) - division's email
+ working_hours (workinghours) - optional field, business hours by each day weekly, doesn't make any influence on business process and will be shown on portal and map.
+ mountain_group: false (boolean)

