                + include Dictionary_v2
                + name: eHealth/ICPC2/condition_codes (string) - Unique dictionary name
                + description: Коди станів за ICPC2 (string) - dictionary description for a user
                + values (array, required)
                    + (Dictionary_value)
                        + code: D88 (string) - code of the dictionary value
                        + description: Апендицит (string) - description of the code

