        + `tax_id` (string, required) - identifier
        + `party_id` (string, required) - identifier
        + `edrpou` (string, required) - identifier
        + `legal_entity_id` (string, required) - identifier
        + `division_id` (string, required) - identifier
        + `status` (string, required) - identifier
        + `employee_type` (string, required) - identifier
        + `page` (string, required) - identifier
        + `page_size` (string, required) - identifier
        + `verification_status` (string, required) - identifier




+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
        Authorization: Bearer c2778f3064753ea70de870a53795f5c9
        X-Custom-PSK: a2aa05c76f3f2d91870f923a53cc8aa8f23bbc01a8238d1c2c26d4299715a7e4

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Response_Collection_V2)

        + data (array[Employee_Short])

