        Authorization: Bearer c2778f3064753ea70de870a53795f5c9
        X-Custom-PSK: a2aa05c76f3f2d91870f923a53cc8aa8f23bbc01a8238d1c2c26d4299715a7e4

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Response_OK)

        + data (Employee_Response)
            + division (Division_Short)
            + legal_entity (Legal_Entity_Short)
                + legal_form: 140 (string) - Business form of legal entity received from edr - Use dictionary LEGAL_FORM to show the name
                + owner_property_type: STATE (string) - Dictionary OWNER_PROPERTY_TYPE
                + mis_verified: VERIFIED, NOT_VERIFIED (string)

