    + Parameters
        + `id` (string, required) - identifier



+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
        Authorization: Bearer c2778f3064753ea70de870a53795f5c9
        api-key: uXhEczJ56adsfh3Ri9SUkc4en
        X-Custom-PSK: a2aa05c76f3f2d91870f923a53cc8aa8f23bbc01a8238d1c2c26d4299715a7e4

    + Attributes (object)

        + include Declaration_Request_Online
        + authorize_with: cc949559-5dfe-420f-ac05-065e443b2cc6 (string)- identifier of person's auth method
        + parent_declaration_id: 8c7753fc-a647-435f-8e43-4ff4546431f6 (string) - identifier of parent declaration in reorganized legal entity

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Response__Process_OK)

        + meta (Response__Meta)
            + code: 201 (number)
        + data (object)
            + id: b075f148-7f93-4fc2-b2ec-2d81b19a9b7b (string)
            + start_date: 2017-03-02 (string) - Should be defined on the client side.
            + end_date: 2017-03-02 (string) - Will be defined on eHealth side if it's not set.
            + person_id: 4d0d790c-cbf1-44f5-ab21-ba8db67da161 (string) - Person ID
            + employee_id: 1a8b10ea-ba09-40f2-8f9e-55608e9208c6 (string) - Employee ID with type=DOCTOR selected from available Employees as a third contract party.
            + division_id: d290f1ee-6c54-4b01-90e6-d701748f0851 (string)
            + declaration_number: 0000-12H4-245D (string) - unique number of declaration.
            + declaration_id: 8311ab82-e341-4da0-8a95-235ec9885e23 (string) - presetted id for future declaration
            + parent_declaration_id: 8c7753fc-a647-435f-8e43-4ff4546431f6 (string) - identifier of parent declaration
            + status: NEW (string)
            + status_reason: not relevant (string) - Dictionary DECLARATION_REQUEST_STATUS_REASON
            + system_declaration_limit: 900 (number) - Current doctor's limit based on speciality_officio
            + current_declaration_count: 675 (number) - Number of declarations assigned to doctor
            + channel: MIS (string) - channel that invoke declaration create service
            + authorize_with: cc949559-5dfe-420f-ac05-065e443b2cc6 (string)- identifier of person's auth method

        + urgent (object)
            + authentication_method_current (object)
                + type: OTP (enum)
                    - OTP
                    - OFFLINE
                    - NA
                + number: +38093*****74 (string)
            + documents (array[media_content], optional)

+ Response 422 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Response_Error)

        + meta (Response__Meta)
            + code: 422
        + error
            + type: unverified (string)
            + message: Person not found (string)

