## Composition [/gen/comp]

### SOAP Get Actual Access Status for Drivers [POST /secret]

+ Request (application/xml)
    + Headers
        SOAPAction: "http://example.com/GetUser"
        Content-Type: text/xml; charset=utf-8

            + Body
            <?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
            <soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/"
                xmlns:urn="http://example.com/">
                <soapenv:Header/>
                <soapenv:Body>
                    <urn:GetUser>
                        <urn:UserID>12345</urn:UserID>
                    </urn:GetUser>
                </soapenv:Body>
            </soapenv:Envelope>

+ Response 200 (application/xml)
            + Body
            <?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
            <soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">
                <soapenv:Body>
                    <GetUserResponse xmlns="http://example.com/">
                        <User>
                            <ID>12345</ID>
                            <Name>John Doe</Name>
                        </User>
                    </GetUserResponse>
                </soapenv:Body>
            </soapenv:Envelope>

